om/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2475808%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%BD%E6%94%BF%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A2019%E3%80%91%E5%88%A9%E5%98%89%E9%96%A3%E6%8C%89%E6%8F%AD%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%9B%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%8C%89%E6%8F%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%9F%E8%87%B340%E5%B9%B4&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVsLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=f296da85\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2475808/【施政報告2019】利嘉閣按揭：望同步放寬按揭年期至40年</a><br />\n<br />\n黃詠欣指近月多家銀行先後上調按息及削減現金回贈，反映銀行在按揭業務利潤微，未來可減息空間細，現時放寬按揭保險計劃的樓價上限，令到用高成數按揭的首置買家的貸款額可大幅上升，若未來息口上升，這群買家的供款壓力會大增，建議可同步放寬貸款年期由30年增至40年，可紓緩供款壓力。"},{"pid":"46e2b97dc4c92efa50c31aed66e74486fffca5ad","tid":1657651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87de9d0bc44f7b571709abbd7dbdbb0cef599c3a","tid":1657651,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bf0651ac143d58042341f6ca0fd03af83b0284a6","tid":1657651,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"吹到老伯父天咁高既青山賤種去晒邊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不服來辯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:09:04.000Z","msg":"青山廢物縮晒入老母個閪度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbff84b652427cde717326505f58e5106235c6b","tid":1657651,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"最撚閪係佢啲信徒<br />\n陳雲講完啲膠野柒野就幫佢兜話唔發癲就冇人理<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140e06892d02f5c562a1da0f34fd6e0e32fb2cc7","tid":1657651,"uid":121197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6f0f5f5fa5850848ccc9aad0d3e76e35e0183286","tid":1657651,"uid":15880,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":